  "text": "<p><span class=\"h-card\" translate=\"no\"><a href=\"https://indieweb.social/@roytang\" class=\"u-url mention\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">@<span>roytang</span></a></span> </p><p>I use FediRedirect<br><a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/fediredirect/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" translate=\"no\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"ellipsis\">addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firef</span><span class=\"invisible\">ox/addon/fediredirect/</span></a><br><a href=\"https://github.com/ManeraKai/fediredirect\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" translate=\"no\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"ellipsis\">github.com/ManeraKai/fediredir</span><span class=\"invisible\">ect</span></a></p><p>It doesn't automatically load the post on my instance<br>1. click the link, opens on original instance<br>2. click the extension button<br>3. wait a second, then choose Redirect &gt; Mastodon</p><p>Then the post loads on my instance</p><p><a href=\"https://ohai.social/tags/Fediverse\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>Fediverse</span></a> <a href=\"https://ohai.social/tags/Mastodon\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>Mastodon</span></a></p>",
